<HEAD>Jesse Jackson Visits Palestinian Youths Hospitalized From Uprising</HEAD>
<HEAD>LaserPhoto CAI1</HEAD>
<DATELINE>CAIRO, Egypt (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   Jesse Jackson on Sunday visited a Palestinian
hospital and shook hands with youths hospitalized with injuries
suffered in the uprising in the Israeli-occupied territories.
   ``We hope that as America looks at this situation, we will look
not only at the politics of the re-elections and of positioning, but
just at the moral obligation to relieve our children of being at
