paralyzed from the waist down, physician Abdel-Kader Shaaban said.
   The Palestine Red Crescent Society, founded in 1968, maintains
branches in several Arab countries and is funded by donations from
the World Health Organization, the Red Cross Society, Arab
organizations and other sources.
   Jackson was in Cairo since Wednesday to attend a meeting of the
U.S. National Council of Negro Women.
